 ## 3. Server-side Access Control
 
 ### Role Assignments
 
-The RBAC module only implements Role Assignments, *not* Roles and Capabilities
-themselves. Role Assignments are stored in the database, and each one contains a
-single role assigned to one user.
+The RBAC module in the Media Server only implements Role Assignments, *not*
+Roles and Capabilities themselves. Role Assignments are stored in the database,
+and each one contains a single role assigned to one user.
 
